com.cyc.base.conn

Class WorkerStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyc.base.conn.WorkerStatus

  • public class WorkerStatus
extends Object

    WorkerStatus is designed to be a type-safe enumeration of the status of a SubLWorker.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static WorkerStatus ABORTED_STATUS
      Indicates that the SubLWorker was aborted.
      static WorkerStatus CANCELED_STATUS
      Indicates that the SubLWorker was canceled.
      static WorkerStatus EXCEPTION_STATUS
      Indicates that the SubLWorker has finished processing the SubL task abnormally because an exception was thrown.
      static WorkerStatus FINISHED_STATUS
      Indicates that the SubLWorker has finished processing the SubL task normally.
      static WorkerStatus NOT_STARTED_STATUS
      Indicates that the SubLWorker has not yet been started.
      static WorkerStatus WORKING_STATUS
      Indicates that the SubLWorker is currently processing the SubL task.
